title: GE Gas Range JGB660SEJSS Tour
description:
In this video we take a look at the features of the GE gas range model JGB660SEJSS.  For more information or to place an order make sure to visit us at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/product/94189/GE-30-Stainless-Steel-Free-Standing-Gas-Range-JGB660SEJSS.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=JGB660SEJSS_20170214&utm_medium=video 

Features:
- Total Capacity (cubic feet): 5.0 cu ft
- Configuration: Range with Storage Drawer
- Ignition System: Electronic
- Oven Cleaning Type: Self-Clean
- Cooktop Burner Type: Sealed
- Cooktop Surface: Edge-to-Edge
- Burner - Left Front: 18,000 BTU Power Boil
- Burner - Left Rear: 5,000 BTU Precise Simmer
- Burner - Right Front: 9,500 BTU
 -Burner - Right Rear: 12,000 BTU
- Burner - Center: 10,000 BTU Oval
- Cooktop Burner Grate Features: Continuous Grates
- Cooktop Burner Grate Material: Heavy Cast Iron
- Control Type: Electronic Touch
- Oven Control Features: Audible Preheat Signal
- Auto Self Clean
- Certified Sabbath Mode
- Control Lock Capability
- Delay Bake Option
- Cooking Technology: Traditional
- Fuel Type: Natural Gas 
- Interior Oven Light: 1 Incandescent
- Oven Rack Features: 2 Oven Racks
